SubjectRegulations Amending the CCOFTA Rules of Origin Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CCOFTA RULES OF ORIGIN REGULATIONS in order to (1) implement updates to the rules of origin under the Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement (CCOFTA); and (2) incorporate by reference any future amendments to the rules of origin provisions under the CCOFTA.
